---
title: Chicken in Rich Mushroom Sauce with Roasted Garlic Broccoli and Zucchini
description: In this lightened-up version of a stroganoff, we’ve topped our beautifully-bronzed chicken thighs and charred roasted broccoli with a luscious mushroom and creme fraiche sauce.
